# Repository Agent Guide

## Working Rules

- Keep changes focused on the issue that triggered the run.
- Read `.issue-to-pr-bot.yml`, `CONTRIBUTING.md`, `README.md`, and templates before implementing.
- If required context is missing, stop instead of guessing.
- Do not commit secrets, tokens, private keys, or local caches.

## Automation Conventions

- Branch format: `bot/{issue_number}{comment_suffix}-{slug}`
- Commit format: `feat(issue-{issue_number}): {issue_title}`
- PR title format: `[bot] #{issue_number} {issue_title}`

## Verification

```powershell
python -m compileall -q app tests
python -m unittest discover -s tests
```

## Protected Paths

- `.github/workflows/**`
- `.env`
- `.env.*`
- `*.pem`
- `*.key`

## Required Context

- `README.md`

## Required Secrets

- `DB_URL`
